# subscript(_:as:)

**Instance Subscript**

Returns the model for the specified identifier, downcast to the appropriate class.

## Declaration

```swift
subscript<T>(id: PersistentIdentifier, as as: T.Type) -> T? where T : PersistentModel { get }
```
